    "Table 3 shows the results and the performance metrics of our proposed models on the CoNaLa dataset.",
    "Also, Table 4 shows the results of those proposed models on the DJANGO dataset.Figures 19 and 20 show these results for the proposed code generation models on the CoNaLa and DJANGO datasets respectively.",
